  "summary": "Race condition in Parc",
  "details": "In the affected versions of this crate, `LockWeak\u003cT\u003e` unconditionally implemented `Send` with no trait bounds on `T`. `LockWeak\u003cT\u003e` doesn't own `T` and only provides `\u0026T`.\n\nThis allows concurrent access to a non-Sync `T`, which can cause undefined behavior like data races.\n",
